data.description: Stately brick raised ranch is located on a beautiful tree lined block and has a large yard. The home features a large spacious living room, three bedrooms, 1.5 baths and a full finished basement with a bath. Great shopping, transportation and schools are nearby. This home is priced to sell!! Lot/room sizes estimated. Cash offers require a minimum 10% earnest money deposit. This property is subject to a 3-Day First Look Period. Seller will negotiate offers after the period expires.
